name: Alice Weidel
description: Alice Weidel and the AfD, supported by Elon Musk, now as a memecoin! Tech mogul Elon Musk has publicly declared his support for the AfD and Alice Weidel. In a live conversation on X, he praised Weidel's vision for Germany and stated that the AfD is the only hope for the country. Alice Weidel, the chancellor candidate of the Alternative for Germany (AfD), stands for conservative values and national sovereignty.
